title: Frigidaire 30in Gas Range FGGF3036BSS
description:
Frigidaire Gallery 30" Stainless Steel Freestanding Gas Range - FGGF3036TF

Features:

Quick Bake Convection 
Bake faster and more evenly with Quick Bake Convection
Steam Cleaning
A 30-minute light oven cleaning that's chemical-free, odor-free, and fast
Power Burner 
Power Burner offers more power and faster boil time with 17,000 BTU burner
One-Touch Quick Self-Clean 
Your oven cleans itself - so you don't have to. Self clean options available in 2- and 3-hour cycles
Smudge-Proof™ Stainless Steel 
Resists fingerprints and cleans easily
Continuous Corner-to-Corner Grates 
Move heavy pots and pans without lifting with continuous, corner-to-corner grates
Low Simmer Burner 
Perfect for cooking delicate foods and sauces
Built with American Pride 
Designed, enginereed and assembled in the U.S.A.
Sabbath Mode (Star-K® Certified)
